
---

# 2️⃣ .gitignore

Create a file named **`.gitignore`**

```gitignore
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Data files (optional)
data/*.pdf

# Model files
*.bin
*.pt

# Environment variables
.env
